      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine starts reliably every time, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, ensuring a comfortable driving experience. The interior is clean with only minor wear, and the exterior maintains a strong finish with just a few small, age-appropriate blemishes. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a solid, pre-owned vehicle.",
