    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in great shape and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth and reliable ride that you can count on. It's a solid, high-quality choice for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks and drives wonderfully. Come see for yourself why this well-cared-for beauty is such a great value!",
