    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for anyone needing a reliable daily commuter. While the exterior shows some minor scratches and the interior has visible wear on the upholstery consistent with its age, the car is mechanically sound. The engine starts up reliably, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. It has been well-maintained under the hood, though a buyer should expect some cosmetic imperfections and perhaps a few minor non-essential repairs in the future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes function over form.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are privileged to offer this impeccably preserved vehicle, which remains in showroom-grade condition. Meticulously maintained and strictly garaged, this specimen exhibits no cosmetic or mechanical imperfections, representing the pinnacle of its class. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands an uncompromising standard of excellence, this acquisition provides an unparalleled opportunity to secure a vehicle in its most pristine form.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
